<manpage>
    <sample url="sdk\operating_system\crt\libc\ctype\isdigit">isdigit</sample>
    <title>isdigit iswdigit</title>
    <volume>C 运行库函数</volume>
    <routine_idx> ctype_idx.htm </routine_idx>

    <description>
        <para>判断一个字符是否为数字字符（‘0’C‘9’）。</para>
    </description>

    <syntax>
        <return_val>int</return_val>
        <func_name>isdigit</func_name>
        <parameters>
            <func_param>
                <param_type>int</param_type>
                <param_name>c</param_name>
                <param_note>
                    <para>待判断的字符</para>
                </param_note>
            </func_param>
        </parameters>
    </syntax>
    
  <syntax>
        <return_val>int</return_val>
        <func_name>iswdigit</func_name>
        <parameters>
            <func_param>
                <param_type>int</param_type>
                <param_name>c</param_name>
         
            </func_param>
        </parameters>
    </syntax>
    <return>
        <para>如果c是一个十进制数字(0-9),则isdigit返回一个非0值。如果c是一个对应于十进制数字字符的宽字符,iswdigit返回一个非0值。如果c不满足这个测试条件则这些例程返回0。</para>
    </return>

    <requirements>
        <routine>
            <routine_name>isdigit</routine_name>
            <headerfile>ctype.h</headerfile>
            <compatibility>ANSI, Windows 2000, Elastos </compatibility>
        </routine>
        <routine>
            <routine_name>iswdigit</routine_name>
            <headerfile>ctype.h</headerfile>
            <compatibility>ANSI, Windows 2000, Elastos </compatibility>
        </routine>
    </requirements>

    <example>
<pre>
//==========================================================================
// Copyright (c) 2000-2008,  Elastos, Inc.  All Rights Reserved.
//==========================================================================

/* isdigit.cpp: This program uses isdigit to verify c
 * whether it is a decimal-digit character(&apos;0&apos; C &apos;9&apos;).
 */

#include &lt;stdio.h&gt;
#include &lt;ctype.h&gt;

int main()
{
    int c = &apos;6&apos;;
    if (isdigit(c)) {
        printf(&quot;c is a decimal-digit character.\n&quot;);
    }
    else {
        printf(&quot;c isn&apos;t a decimal-digit character.\n&quot;);
    }

    return 0;
}
</pre>
    </example>
<result>
c is a decimal-digit character.
</result>



